snippet.textDisplay: i’m from bangladesh and I’ve been wishing to visit Pakistan someday as i had a few of childhood friends living in there. I wasn’t a fan of coke studios before but after listening to this song, I started to regret what I could have missed if i would’ve have listened to this song from my suggestion. This song is just outstanding and heart soothing 😍 and the duo just took it to a new level. Rahat sir is a living legend but for the first time,after listening to such vocal from momina , I eagerly want to visit pakistan any time sooner from now on to listen to her voice and see her live 😍. May my wish come true and best wishes for momina and rahat sir.
